"There is some stock of Buckets and Dispensers so no need to order some for "
"the ongoing\n"
"        period.<br/>However, you need to order Mayonnaise Buckets to meet "
"your forecast!"
msgstr ""
"Tenemos stock de baldes y dispensadores, por lo que no necesitamos ordenar "
"más para el periodo\n"
"        en curso.<br/>Sin embargo, sí necesitas ordenar baldes de mayonesa "
"para cumplir con tu pronóstico."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There now is a smart button at the top of the Purchase Order to reach the "
"associated\n"
"        delivery. Hit the Deliveries smart button to open the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Ahora hay un botón inteligente en la parte superior de la orden de compra "
"para acceder a la\n"
"        entrega asociada. Haz clic en el botón inteligente de entregas para "
"abrir la entrega."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
